message.body: Welcome back, boo boo! I'm so excited to SEE YOU and hear all about it. When do you get in? Want to make dinner tomorrow night before open mic?
Hey hun!! Yes absolutely! You should come to my place because I'm required to watch The Voice with my sister! My flight is a bit delayed so I won't be in
The voice tomorrow night? Jason is having people meet him since he's in town! He sent the message after I texted you
Oh shit!! Lemme look at it.
We don't have to go to jasons thing... It sounds sort of cray cray
Hey sweets. I don't think Jesse can play anymore so no worries on that. When and where is the concert?
Fine line! We can go at like 8 or 830 if you wanna!
Mmmmk! That sounds good. I think tim is going to come with too if that's cool. Did you say youre picking me up? Or do you want to meet?
